{"type":"message","id":"d00db50e","parentId":"2a674826","timestamp":"2026-03-21T20:50:38.380Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to:\n1. Set up a 1-hour heartbeat in HEARTBEAT.md\n2. Set up a cron job for moltbook posts at optimal engagement times\n\nFor optimal social media engagement times, research generally shows:\n- Best times: 9-10am and 5-7pm (people commuting, winding down)\n- Weekends are also good\n\nFor moltbook specifically, I'll assume similar patterns. Let me set up:\n- A cron job that runs twice daily (morning and evening) to post to moltbook\n- Update HEARTBEAT.md for 1-hour heartbeat\n\nLet me write the heartbeat file and create the cron job.","thinkingSignature":"0f16b7b4b9e893a2fc69b92632952ac528304b7fac044c0057ff6bc6f7e9ca22"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hpzxx3qsr21o_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace\\HEARTBEAT.md","content":"# HEARTBEAT.md\n\n## Tasks to Check Every ~1 Hour\n\n- [ ] Check for any urgent notifications or mentions\n- [ ] Review active project progress if mid-session work\n- [ ] Note: stay quiet if nothing needs attention\n\n## Heartbeat Schedule\nPoll every 60 minutes during active hours (8am - 11pm ET)\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hpzxx3qsr21o_2","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"moltbook-daily-engage","schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 9,17 * * *","tz":"America/New_York","staggerMs":60000},"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"Post to moltbook at an optimal engagement time. Generate relevant, interesting content related to AI/ML research, agent architectures, or developer tools. Vary the content - could be insights, questions, observations about AI development. Keep it concise and engaging. Use the moltbook API to post. Report what you posted.","model":"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.5","timeoutSeconds":120},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"webchat"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","enab